title: Five Guys, Portillo's, AND Another Olive Garden?? | Mark Manuel | Q106.5
text:
Five Guys, Portillo's, AND Another Olive Garden?? posted by Mark Manuel - share 
Flipped on Good Morning Quad Cities today on channel 8 and they were doing their "Breakfast With..." segment. Their guest, Ray Forsythe, Planning and Development Director of the City of Moline, said that plans ARE in the works for a Portillo's (apparently, the CEO is from Moline, so we kind of have an "in"), another Olive Garden (on the Illinois side)...AND THIS IS THE ONE I'M SUPER EXCITED ABOUT...not one but TWO Five Guys Burgers And Fries, one on each side of the river! Yes, I am THAT Mark Manuel...AKA "Malibu" Mark Manuel from my days on All Hit 98-9. Early in my career, I worked at KGGO in Des Moines...so I feel right at home on Q106.5. PLUS...this is the rock 'n' roll that I grew up with! Contact
